preference.name: DuplicateAssignToProject
preference.preference_description: Controls the status of the Assign Projects to New Items check box in the Duplicate... dialog box for duplicating Systems Engineering requirement structures. If the preference is set to true, the Assign Projects to New Items check box is selected and the section under the Projects header is expanded in the Duplicate... dialog box. Valid Values: true false
